      "text": "Host Memory\n(Pageable)\n\n• 普通 malloc\n• 可交换到磁盘\n• H2D 需先拷贝到\n  Pinned Memory",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Host Memory\n(Pageable)\n\n• 普通 malloc\n• 可交换到磁盘\n• H2D 需先拷贝到\n  Pinned Memory",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.4020408163265308
    },
